        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">3. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          This Site is provided "as is" without warranties. Hustle & Rise makes no representations about the Site's operation, content, or materials.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          Hustle & Rise is not liable for damages or losses from using this Site, including indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">5. Business & Income Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          <strong>IMPORTANT:</strong> Content on Hustle & Rise is educational only. Results vary. We make no income guarantees. Past performance doesn't guarantee future results. All business ventures carry risk, including financial loss. You are responsible for your own decisions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          All content on this Site—text, graphics, logos, images, software—is protected by copyright. Reproduction without permission is prohibited.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">7. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          This Site may link to external websites. We're not responsible for their content or practices. Your use is at your own risk.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">8. Modification of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          Hustle & Rise reserves the right to update these Terms at any time. Continued use means you accept the changes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-brand text-2xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4 text-white tracking-wide">9. Termination</h2>
        <p class="text-white/70 mb-6">
          Hustle & Rise may suspend or terminate your access at any time, with or without cause.
        </p>

